00:47:09.150 --> 00:47:10.920
It's just a matter of telling
the machine how many times

00:47:10.920 --> 00:47:14.390
to lay it down, and you can
make it, you can take a plate

00:47:14.390 --> 00:47:18.220
and make 100 at time if you want.

00:47:18.220 --> 00:47:22.500
In our first presentation of
this project, Sina demonstrated

00:47:22.500 --> 00:47:27.370
that the micro CT and additive
manufacture copies were actually

00:47:27.370 --> 00:47:31.100
