00:56:16.600 --> 00:56:18.470 position:56%
The tip opening on the sax original.

00:56:18.470 --> 00:56:21.460
Go back to that slide I showed you
of saxophone mouthpiece anatomy.

00:56:21.460 --> 00:56:23.770 position:56%
