00:56:33.180 --> 00:56:35.340
but it enriches their sound.

00:56:35.340 --> 00:56:38.970
So, the tenor and the soprano
also required narrower reeds

00:56:38.970 --> 00:56:40.270
than are sold today.

00:56:40.270 --> 00:56:41.570
And, I was fortunate to have a box

