00:57:04.000 --> 00:57:07.750
And so, I got some measurements
just with calipers, not with CT.

00:57:07.750 --> 00:57:12.240
I was very pleased to find that
our measurements for the alto

00:57:12.240 --> 00:57:17.140
and the baritone agreed within a
few percent with Sax's original.

00:57:17.140 --> 00:57:21.590
For the soprano, however, Sax
didn't follow his own advice.

00:57:21.590 --> 00:57:25.110
He didn't simply scale
down, scale down the bass.

